characters.name: Sung Jinwoo
characters.description: An E-rank hunter known for being weak and frequently injured, who receives mysterious daily quests.

characters.name: Park
characters.description: A hunter who exchanges greetings with Park and provides information about Jinwoo Sung and raid safety.

characters.name: The Ultimate Hunter
characters.description: A title referring to the S-rank hunter Jongin Choi.

characters.name: Joohee Lee
characters.description: A healer who frequently treats Jinwoo's injuries and expresses concern for his safety.

characters.name: Song
characters.description: A hunter with ten years of experience, a fire spell specialist, and the de facto leader of the party exploring the double dungeon.
